quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  30,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  30,1,Alif Laaam Meeem
  30,2,( ehley ) room maghloob hogaye
  30,3,nazdeek ke malik mein aur woh maghloob honay ke baad anqareeb ghalib ajayeen ge
  30,4,chand hi saal mein pehlay bhi aur peechay bhi khuda hi ka hukum hai aur uss roz momin khush ho jaien ge
  30,5,( yani ) khuda ki madad se. woh jisay chahta hai madad deta hai aur woh ghalib ( aur ) meharban hai
  30,6,( yeh ) khuda ka wada ( hai ) khuda apne waday ke khilaaf nahi karta lekin aksar log nahi jantay
  30,7,yeh to duniya ki zahiri zindagi ko jantay hain. aur akhirat ( ki taraf ) se ghaafil hain
  30,8,kiya onhon ne apne dil mein ghhor nahikiya. ke khuda ne asmano aur zameen ko aur jo kuch un dono ke darmain hai unn ko hikmat se aur aik waqt muqarrar taq ke liye pedakiya hai. aur bohat se log apne perwar-digaar se milnay ke qaail hi nahi
  30,9,kiya unn logon ne malik mein sair nahi ki ( sair karte ) to dekh letay ke jo log unn se pehlay they un ka injaam kaisay howa. woh unn se zoro qowat mein kahin ziyada they aur onhon ne zameen ko joota aur is ko is se ziyada abadkiya tha jo onhon ne abadkiya. aur unn ke paas unn ke paighambar nishanain le kar atay rahay to khuda aisa nah tha ke unn par zulm karta. balkay wohi apne aap par zulm karte they
  30,10,phir jin logon ne buraiee ki unn ka injaam bhi bura howa is liye ke khuda ki aayton ko jutlatay aur unn ki hansi uratye rahay they
  30,11,khuda hi khalqat ko pehli baar peda karta hai wohi is ko phir peda kere ga phir tum usi ki taraf lout jao ge
  30,12,aur jis din qayamat barpaa hogi gunehgaar na umeed ho jaien ge
  30,13,aur un ke ( banaye hue ) sharikon mein se koi un ka safarishi nah hoga aur woh apne sharikon se نامعتقد ho jaien ge
  30,14,aur jis din qayamat barpaa hogi is roz woh allag allag firqay ho jaien ge
  30,15,to jo log imaan laaye aur amal naik karte rahay woh ( bahisht ke ) baagh mein khush haal hon ge
  30,16,aur jinhon ne kufarkiya aur hamari aayton aur akhirat ke anay ko jhtlaya. woh azaab mein daaley jayen ge
  30,17,to jis waqt tum ko shaam ho aur jis waqt subah ho khuda ki tasbeeh karo ( yani namaz parho )
  30,18,aur asmano aur zameen mein usi ki tareef hai. aur teesray pehar bhi aur jab dopehar ho ( uss waqt bhi namaz parha karo )
  30,19,wohi zinday ko murdy se nkalta aur ( wohi ) murdy ko zinday se nkalta hai aur ( wohi ) zameen ko is ke marnay ke baad zindah karta hai. aur isi terhan tum ( dobarah zameen mein se ) nikalay jao ge
  30,20,aur isi ke nishanaat ( aur tasarufaat ) mein se hai ke uss ne tumhe matti se pedakiya. phir ab tum ensaan hokar ja baja phail rahay ho
  30,21,aur isi ke nishanaat ( aur tasarufaat ) mein se hai ke uss ne tumahray liye tumhari hi jins ki aurtain peda kee taakay unn ki taraf ( mael hokar ) aaraam haasil karo aur tum mein mohabbat aur meharbani peda kar di jo log ghhor karte hain unn ke liye un baton mein ( bohat si ) nishanain hain
  30,22,aur isi ke nishanaat ( aur tasarufaat ) mein se hai asmano aur zameen ka peda karna aur tumhari zabanon aur rangon ka judda judda hona. ehley Danish ke liye un ( baton ) mein ( bohat si ) nishanain hain
  30,23,aur isi ke nishanaat ( aur tasarufaat ) mein se hai tumhara raat aur din mein sona aur uss ke fazl ka talaash karna. jo log suntay hain unn ke liye un baton mein ( bohat si ) nishanain hain
  30,24,aur isi ke nishanaat ( aur tasarufaat ) mein se hai ke tum ko khauf aur umeed dilanay ke liye bijli dekhata hai aur aasman semeinhہ brsata hai. phir zameen ko is ke mar jaane ke baad zindah ( o shadaab ) kar deta hai. aqal walon ke liye un ( baton ) mein ( bohat si ) nishanain hain
  30,25,aur isi ke nishanaat ( aur tasarufaat ) mein se hai ke aasman aur zameen is ke hukum se qaim hain. phir jab woh tum ko zameen mein se ( niklny ke liye ) aawaz day ga to tum jhat nikal parro ge
  30,26,aur asmano aur zameen mein ( jitne farishtay aur ensaan waghera hain ) isi ke ( mamlook ) hain ( aur ) tamam is ke farmanbardar hain
  30,27,aur wohi to hai jo khalqat ko pehli dafaa peda karta hai phir ussay dobarah peda kere ga. aur yeh is ko bohat aasaan hai. aur asmano aur zameen mein is ki shaan bohat buland hai. aur woh ghalib hikmat wala hai
  30,28,"woh tumahray liye tumahray hi haal ki aik misaal bayan farmata hai ke bhala jin ( londi ghulamoo ) ke tum maalik ho woh is ( maal ) mein jo hum ne tum ko ataa farmaya hai tumahray shareek hain, aur (kiya ) tum is mein ( unn ko apne ) barabar ( maalik samajte ) ho ( aurkiya ) tum unn se is terhan drtay ho jis terhan apnon se drtay ho, isi terhan aqal walon ke liye apni ayatain khol khol kar bayan karte hain"
  30,29,magar jo zalim hain be samjhay apni khawahishon ke peechay chaltay hain to jis ko khuda gumraah kere ussay kon hadaayat day sakta hai? aur un ka koi madadgaar nahi
  30,30,to tum aik taraf ke hokar deen ( khuda ke raste ) par seedha munh kiye chalay jao ( aur ) khuda ki fitrat ko jis par uss ne logon ko pedakiya hai ( ikhtiyar kiye raho ) khuda ki banai hui ( fitrat ) mein tagayur o tabdeel nahi ho sakta. yahi seedha deen hai lekin aksar log nahi jantay
  30,31,( momino ) usi ( khuda ) ki taraf rujoo kiye raho aur is se drtay raho aur namaz parhte raho aur mushrikon mein nah hona
  30,32,( aur nah ) unn logon mein ( hona ) jinhon ne apne deen ko tukre tukre kar diya aur ( khud ) firqay firqay ho gay. sab firqay isi se khush hain jo unn ke paas hai
  30,33,aur jab logon ko takleef pahunchti hai to apne perwar-digaar ko pkarte aur isi ki taraf rujoo hotay hain. phir jab woh un ko apni rehmat ka maza chkhata hai to aik firqa unn mein se apne perwar-digaar se shirk karne lagta hai
  30,34,taakay jo hum ne un ko bakhsha hai uss ki nashukri karen so ( kher ) faiday اutha loo anqareeb tum ko ( is ka injaam ) maloom ho jaye ga
  30,35,kiya hum ne un par koi aisi Daleel nazil ki hai ke unn ko khuda ke sath shirk karna batati hai
  30,36,aur jab hum logon ko apni rehmat ka maza chukhate hain to uss se khush ho jatay hain aur agar unn ke amlon ke sabab jo unn ke hathon ne agay beje hain koi gznd puhanche to na umeed ho kar reh jatay hain
  30,37,kiya onhon ne nahi dekha ke khuda hi jis ke liye chahta hai rizaq farakh karta hai aur ( jis ke liye chahta hai ) tang karta hai. bay shak is mein imaan laane walon ke liye nishanain hain
  30,38,to ehley qaraabat aur mohtajon aur musafiron ko un ka haq dete raho. jo log razaye khuda ke taalib hain yeh unn ke haq mein behtar hai. aur yahi log nijaat haasil karne walay hain
  30,39,aur jo tum sood dete ho ke logon ke maal mein afzaish ho to khuda ke nazdeek is mein afzaish nahi hoti aur jo tum zakaat dete ho aur uss se khuda ki Raza mandi talab karte ho to ( woh mojab barket hai aur ) aisay hi log ( apne maal ko ) do chand sah chand karne walay hain
  30,40,khuda hi to hai jis ne tum ko pedakiya phir tum ko rizaq diya phir tumhe maaray ga. phir zindah kere ga. bhala tumahray ( banaye hue ) sharikon mein bhi koi aisa hai jo un kamon mein se kuch kar sakay. woh pak hai aur ( is ki shaan ) un ke sharikon se buland hai
  30,41,khushki aur tri mein logon ke aamaal ke sabab fasaad phail gaya hai taakay khuda unn ko unn ke baaz aamaal ka maza chakha-ay ajab nahi ke woh baz ajayeen
  30,42,keh do ke malik mein chalo phiro aur dekho ke jo log ( tum se ) pehlay hue hain un ka kaisa injaam howa hai. un mein ziyada tar mushriq hi they
  30,43,to is roz se pehlay jo khuda ki taraf se aakar rahay ga aur ruk nahi sakay ga deen ( ke raste ) par seedha munh kiye chalay chalo is roz ( sab ) log munhtashir ho jaien ge
  30,44,jis shakhs ne kufarkiya to is ke kufar ka zarrar usi ko hai aur jis ne naik amal kiye to aisay log apne hi liye aaraam gaah durust karte hain
  30,45,jo log imaan laaye aur naik amal karte rahay unn ko khuda apne fazl se badla day ga. bay shak woh kafiroon ko dost nahi rakhta
  30,46,aur usi ki nshanyon mein se hai ke hawaon ko bhejta hai ke khushkhabri deti hain taakay tum ko apni rehmat ke mazay chakha-ay aur taakay is ke hukum se kashtiyan chalein aur taakay is ke fazl se ( rozi ) talab karo ajab nahi ke tum shukar karo
  30,47,aur hum ne tum se pehlay bhi paighambar un ki qoum ki taraf beje to woh unn ke paas nishanain le kar aeye so jo log nafarmani karte they hum ne unn se badla le kar chorra aur mominoun ki madad hum par lazim thi
  30,48,khuda hi to hai jo hawaon ko chalata hai to woh baadal ko abharti hain. phir khuda is ko jis terhan chahta hai aasman mein phela deta aur teh-ba-teh kar deta hai phir tum dekhte ho ke is ke beech mein semeinhہ niklny lagta hai phir jab woh apne bundon mein se jin par chahta hai ussay barsa deta hai to woh khush ho jatay hain
  30,49,aur beshtar to wohmeinhہ ke aُtrne se pehlay na umeed ho rahay they
  30,50,to ( ae dekhnay walay ) khuda ki rehmat ki nshanyon ki taraf dekh ke woh kis terhan zameen ko is ke marnay ke baad zindah karta hai. bay shak woh mardon ko zindah karne wala hai. aur woh har cheez par Qadir hai
  30,51,aur agar hum aisi howa bhejen ke woh ( is ke sabab ) khaiti ko dekhen ( ke ) zard ( ho gayi hai ) to is ke baad woh nashukri karne lag jayen
  30,52,to tum mardon ki ( baat ) nahi suna satke aur nah behroon ko jab woh peeth phair kar phir jayen aawaz suna satke ho
  30,53,aur nah andhon ko unn ki gumraahi se ( nikaal kar ) raah raast par laskte ho. tum to unhi logon ko suna satke ho jo hamari aayton par imaan laatay hain so wohi farmanbardar hain
  30,54,khuda hi to hai jis ne tum ko ( ibtida mein ) kamzor haalat mein pedakiya phir kamzoree ke baad taaqat inayat ki phir taaqat ke baad kamzoree aur burhapa diya. woh jo chahta hai peda karta hai aur woh sahib Danish aur sahib qudrat hai
  30,55,aur jis roz qayamat barpaa hogi gunehgaar kasmain khayen ge ke woh ( duniya mein ) aik gharri se ziyada nahi rahay they. isi terhan woh ( raste se ) ultay jatay they
  30,56,aur jin logon ko ilm aur imaan diya gaya tha woh kahin ge ke khuda ki kitaab ke mutabiq tum qayamat taq rahay ho. aur yeh qayamat hi ka din hai lekin tum ko is ka yaqeen hi nahi tha
  30,57,to is roz zalim logon ko un ka izr kuch faida nah day ga aur nah unn se tauba qubool ki jaye gi
  30,58,aur hum ne logon ke ( samjhane ke ) liye is quran mein har terhan ki misaal bayan kar di hai aur agar tum unn ke samnay koi nishani paish karo to yeh kafir keh den ge ke tum to jhutay ho
  30,59,isi terhan khuda unn logon ke dilon par jo samajh nahi rakhtay mohar laga deta hai
  30,60,pas tum sabr karo bay shak khuda ka wada sacha hai aur ( dekho ) jo log yaqeen nahi rakhtay woh tumhe oocha nah bnadin
